column7: Good quick meal near the train station
column9: With an hour before my train left, this restaurant gave a good "Californian-style" meal. The vegetarian fajitas were nicely done and the surroundings are an ok attempt at giving the feel of being in California.
I got a nice café latte for 30 sek by a nice talkative bartender girl.
Popular among young people - good for students who want a drink and quick bite. Wraps average - a fast food place close to the station.
Food is ok, nothing special but it's more than adequate. Big plus is the size of the portions - they are huge.
